casebody.data:
No. 65,

Orig.

Texas v. New Mexico.

Motion of the River Master for fees and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the River Master is awarded a total of $2,439 for the period January 1 through March 31,2000, to be paid equally by the parties. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 528 U. S. 925.]
